发信人: leonking (大自在天), 信区: Game<br />标  题: 这才是真正的大作啊<br />发信站: 水木社区 (Wed Jul  9 05:11:48 2008), 站内<br /><br />什么百万级大作，千万级神作，统统一边去。这个是每代目标直指一亿的游戏啊。<br /><br />刚刚查了一下，原来SIMS系列在欧美是如此可怕的游戏怪物。从2000年问世以来 SIMS 1 <br />加上资料片买了7千万份以上， SIMS 2 和资料片更是3年就有1 亿以上的销量。连家用机<br />老任的马里奥都望尘莫及的数据啊，除了传说中无法估计的俄罗斯方块，怕它就是世界游<br />戏界的老大了，EA靠它一个游戏就够了。<br /><br />http://www.eurogamer.net/article.php?article_id=94927<br /><br />Consider this: the original Sims sold over fifty million copies during its <br />lifespan. You can slap at least another twenty million on that figure once <br />you throw in the expansion packs. The Sims 2 and its add-ons sailed over the <br />hundred million sales threshold in three years. While its domesticated <br />structure may leave many boy gamers confused and angry and oh-so-insecure, <br />The Sims is inarguably one of the most important and successful games <br />franchises of the 21st century. And now The Sims 3 is bearing down on us, <br />like an impeccably-dressed steamroller with a green diamond floating on top, <br />so let's see how it all began.<br /><br />明年发售的SIMS 3怕又是要秒杀一切其他游戏了，唉<br /><br />顺便贴下暴雪的游戏销量：<br /><br /># World of Warcraft (10 million subscribers) 一千万<br /><br />* World of Warcraft: The Burning Crusade [expansion pack] (3.5 million) 三百五<br />十万<br /><br /># StarCraft (9.5 million, may include StarCraft: Brood War) 九百五十万<br /><br /># Diablo II (4 million) 四百万<br /><br />* Diablo II: Lord of Destruction [expansion pack] (1 million;2 million <br />shipped) 二百万<br /><br /># Warcraft III: Reign of Chaos (3 million) 三百万<br /><br />* Warcraft III: The Frozen Throne [expansion pack] (1 million) 一百万<br /><br /># Diablo (2.5 million)[189] 二百五十万<br /><br /><br />我看除非中国人都开始买暴雪的正版，要不然暴雪这辈子拍马都赶不上EA了。别说EA了，<br />恐怕暴雪所有游戏加一起想赶上SIMS这个系列的任何一代都难啊。<br /><br />--<br />我只是一只土土的小青蛙，苟活于来往的恐龙留下的足印中。一天，我正在睡午觉，一只<br />小恐龙追随她前辈JJ的足迹走了过来。于是我终于圆满了。。。<br /><br /><br />※ 来源:·水木社区 newsmth.net·[FROM: 68.40.192.*]